Class CheckInventoryRequest

  • java.lang.Object
    • myfuel.Request.Request
      • myfuel.Request.CheckInventoryRequest
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class CheckInventoryRequest
extends Request
    This class will be used as a request from the server for 2 things: 1. Request for checking if there is any inventory order for specific station 2. Request for updating station inventory (depends if there was any inventory order)
